WEBVTT

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.990
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.309
joining us again tonight. We're excited

00:00:06.319 --> 00:00:08.070
to pray with y'all. We have some

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:10.230
things I want to share with you. First,

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:12.390
all glory to Jesus. We have no

00:00:12.390 --> 00:00:12.400
incidents

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.870
today at all. And I just want

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.750
to give God praise right now. I believe

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:20.790
it's the fervent prayers of the

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:23.429
righteous that avail much. It's

00:00:23.439 --> 00:00:26.150
because of you and me,

00:00:26.150 --> 00:00:26.160
and

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.070
other prayer groups around the United

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:29.990
States, that we're praying and

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.509
changing things through the power of

00:00:31.519 --> 00:00:34.389
prayer and the authority of the believer.

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:37.030
We're able to pray for the shopping,

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.790
that there were no casualties. We only

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.030
had one major incident. We pray for the

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:42.950
family

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:45.910
that lost their daughter in the tragic,

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:47.029
terrible

00:00:47.039 --> 00:00:50.389
incident in Washington the day

00:00:50.399 --> 00:00:53.430
before Thanksgiving. That was awful.

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.270
And she went home; I pray she knew

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:57.830
Jesus Christ. That's why

00:00:57.840 --> 00:00:59.510
I try to tell you all the time,

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.590
none of us are promised tomorrow. I'm

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.910
sure she didn't know that

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:05.830
day that

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:08.070
she would pass away and that the tragic

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:09.670
thing was going to happen. You never

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:11.830
want to take this time for

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.510
granted.

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.270
Always look at the now. Thank God that

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:18.230
we have now and give your heart to

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:21.590
Jesus Christ. You must know Him.

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:24.310
You must know that tomorrow's not

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:27.749
promised. We pray for her family and

00:01:27.749 --> 00:01:27.759
for

00:01:27.759 --> 00:01:30.789
the loss. I don't know

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:32.469
if she had children or what,

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:34.310
but that was a very sad situation. I

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:35.670
don't know if the other man passed away,

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.230
but

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:41.270
thank God it was not more.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:43.749
Thank God that today we didn't see

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:48.069
anything. I still have an urgency

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:51.030
to pray over the shopping all through

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:53.910
this season. Continually praying over

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:57.109
the economy, our

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:59.990
nation, the nation's capital, and

00:01:59.990 --> 00:02:00.000
the

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.709
White House tree

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.230
ceremony with

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:06.389
the lighting of the tree. Praying over

00:02:06.399 --> 00:02:09.430
the Rockefeller Times Square tree

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:09.440
ceremony—that's

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:11.190
why that's behind us

00:02:11.190 --> 00:02:11.200
tonight—and

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:13.910
continually

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:16.869
lifting up New Year's Eve and all the

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:20.229
holiday season, that no weapon formed

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:22.949
against this nation shall prosper.

00:02:22.959 --> 00:02:24.710
You always get the

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:26.869
critics who say, 'Well, Brandon, don't

00:02:26.879 --> 00:02:29.110
