00:03:16.239 --> 00:03:17.990
him, I'm still

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.589
looking into that. You don't

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:22.070
know what's fake news and what's real

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:23.910
news. So, I just try not to get into the

00:03:23.920 --> 00:03:25.750
conspiracies.

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:30.470
I want to start off with

00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:33.509
this,

00:03:33.519 --> 00:03:36.710
and this is my opinion.

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:38.630
Everything that I say about this is my

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:40.149
opinion, and it's not me telling you to

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:42.550
do anything. I want you to pray about

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:44.869
