00:03:50.229 --> 00:03:50.239
just

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:54.070
what

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:56.550
my wife and I do. We believe this,

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.390
but I do not bring it up very

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:00.470
