phone today, and she was talking about

00:04:02.239 --> 00:04:03.990
some of the things she

00:04:03.990 --> 00:04:04.000
and

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:07.270
my extended

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:10.070
family do. I thought,

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:12.550
'Well,

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.309
I don't like talking about this stuff

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:16.229
because a lot of people do

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:18.069
