00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.710
circles that we're

00:04:20.710 --> 00:04:20.720
in.'But

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.150
I'm going to talk about

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.550
it. I think it's wisdom sometimes just

