00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:43.510
I want to talk to you about wheat

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:47.350
and making homemade

00:04:47.350 --> 00:04:47.360
breads—shelf

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:50.310
