00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:52.310
You don't have to do this, but this

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:55.110
is what Diana and I do. We believe in

00:04:55.120 --> 00:05:00.230
making this wheat.

00:05:00.230 --> 00:05:00.240
It's

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:04.150
just grains, but we've bought

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:07.189
