00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:05.510
fresh muffins, fresh tortillas.

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:08.629
This has shelf

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:10.950
life for the end times.

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:13.350
You don't ever have to worry.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:18.390
We had friends talk to us about it.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:22.150
I was asking God for an

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:24.550
alternative to

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:24.560
that

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:27.510
survival food a big ministry in

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:30.550
Branson sells.

00:06:32.080 --> 00:06:34.070
I was looking

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:36.950
at the content inside these

00:06:36.950 --> 00:06:36.960
buckets,

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:41.189
this 30-year shelf-life food,

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:44.070
and in the natural,

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:45.909
folks, you maybe could eat it for a

00:06:45.919 --> 00:06:47.830
