00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:50.790
This stuff is bad.

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:55.670
I know what the Father has told me is coming,

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:58.390
and I know He's extended

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:00.629
