00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:17.830
don't

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:20.230
like, like I said, the 30-year

00:07:20.230 --> 00:07:20.240
shelf-life

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:22.390
food. It's not healthy. But wheat

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:24.710
lasts if you have

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:26.710
these tubs and

00:07:26.710 --> 00:07:26.720
tighten the

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:28.950
lid

00:07:32.309 --> 00:07:32.319
to

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:36.309
