You can grind up the wheat and make

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:41.830
fresh breads

00:07:41.830 --> 00:07:41.840
to

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:44.309
take care

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:45.749
of your family.

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:47.830
You can find YouTube videos if

00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:51.110
