00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:07.589
I try to think of

00:08:07.599 --> 00:08:09.749
how you stay alive and take

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:11.430
care of yourself if things were to

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:15.270
